    2. Compute pointwise multiplication:
       $ (p compose q)(omega^j) = p(omega^j) q(omega^j) $ for $j = 0, dots, 2n-1$
       Time: $O(n)$

    3. Interpolate $p compose q$ using inverse DFT to obtain coefficients $c_0, c_1, dots, c_(2n-2)$. Time: $O(n log n)$
